{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012QPrzhgceEK11NYLZedMXM","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have now read all the critical files. Let me create a comprehensive summary organized by package. This is a complete Jakarta EE petclinic application that I've thoroughly reviewed.\n\n---\n\n## COMPLETE FILE INVENTORY - JAKARTA EE PETCLINIC APPLICATION\n\nI've successfully read ALL Java source files and configuration files from the Jakarta EE Petclinic application. Below is the complete organized inventory:\n\n---\n\n## 1. APPLICATION CONFIGURATION\n\n### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java\n- Main JAX-RS Application class\n- Extends `jakarta.ws.rs.core.Application`\n- Annotated with `@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")` - defines REST API base path\n- ApplicationScoped CDI bean\n- Contains MessageProvider for i18n\n\n### /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageProvider.java\n- Provides access to resource bundles for i18n\n- Uses FacesContext for JSF integration\n\n---\n\n## 2. ENTITY CLASSES (JPA Entities)\n\n### Owner Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `owner`\n- Fields: id, uuid, firstName, lastName, address, houseNumber, addressInfo, city, zipCode, phoneNumber, email, searchindex\n- Validation: @NotEmpty, @Email, @Pattern for phone/zipcode\n- Named Queries: `Owner.getAll`, `Owner.search`\n- Sequence: `owner_seq`\n- Unique constraints on uuid, email, and combination of names+city+phone\n\n### Pet Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `owner_pet`\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, birthDate, type (ManyToOne to PetType), owner (ManyToOne to Owner), searchindex\n- Named Queries: `Pet.getAll`, `Pet.getPetsAsList`\n- Sequence: `owner_pet_seq`\n- Relationships: EAGER fetch for both type and owner\n\n### PetType Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `owner_pet_pettype`\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, searchindex\n- Named Queries: `PetType.getAll`, `PetType.findByName`, `PetType.search`\n- Sequence: `owner_pet_pettype_seq`\n- Static factory methods: `newEntity()`, `newEntity(String name)`\n\n### Specialty Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `specialty`\n- Fields: id, uuid, name, searchindex\n- Named Queries: `Specialty.getAll`, `Specialty.findSpecialtyByName`, `Specialty.search`\n- Sequence: `specialty_seq`\n- Static factory methods: `newEntity()`, `newEntity(String name)`\n\n### Vet Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `vet`\n- Fields: id, uuid, firstName, lastName, specialties (ManyToMany with Specialty), searchindex\n- Named Queries: `Vet.getAll`, `Vet.search`\n- Sequence: `vet_seq`\n- Join Table: `vet_specialties` with columns `vet_id` and `specialty_id`\n- EAGER fetch for specialties\n\n### Visit Entity\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java`\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Table: `owner_pet_visit`\n- Fields: id, uuid, date, description, pet (ManyToOne to Pet), searchindex\n- Named Queries: `Visit.getAll`, `Visit.getVisits`\n- Sequence: `owner_pet_visit_seq`\n- EAGER fetch for pet\n\n---\n\n## 3. REST ENDPOINTS (JAX-RS Resources)\n\nAll endpoints are annotated with `@Stateless` EJB and use `@EJB` injection.\n\n### OwnerEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/owner/list` - Returns JSON list of owners\n- GET `/rest/owner/{id}` - Returns JSON owner by id\n- GET `/rest/owner/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/owner/{id}+json` - Returns JSON owner\n- GET `/rest/owner/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/owner/{id}+xml` - Returns XML owner\n\n### PetEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/pet/list` - Returns JSON list of pets\n- GET `/rest/pet/{id}` - Returns JSON pet by id\n- GET `/rest/pet/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/pet/{id}+json` - Returns JSON pet\n- GET `/rest/pet/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/pet/{id}+xml` - Returns XML pet\n\n### PetTypeEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/petType/list` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/petType/{id}` - Returns JSON pet type\n- GET `/rest/petType/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/petType/{id}+json` - Returns JSON pet type\n- GET `/rest/petType/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/petType/{id}+xml` - Returns XML pet type\n\n### SpecialtyEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/specialty/list` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/specialty/{id}` - Returns JSON specialty\n- GET `/rest/specialty/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/specialty/{id}+json` - Returns JSON specialty\n- GET `/rest/specialty/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/specialty/{id}+xml` - Returns XML specialty\n\n### VetEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/vet/list` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/vet/{id}` - Returns JSON vet\n- GET `/rest/vet/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/vet/{id}+json` - Returns JSON vet\n- GET `/rest/vet/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/vet/{id}+xml` - Returns XML vet\n\n### VisitEndpoint\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java`\n\n**Operations:**\n- GET `/rest/visit/list` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/visit/{id}` - Returns JSON visit\n- GET `/rest/visit/list+json` - Returns JSON list\n- GET `/rest/visit/{id}+json` - Returns JSON visit\n- GET `/rest/visit/list+xml` - Returns XML list\n- GET `/rest/visit/{id}+xml` - Returns XML visit\n\n---\n\n## 4. DT