__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBase.java`\n  - Base interface for all entities with getId, getUuid, getPrimaryKey, updateSearchindex\n- **EntityBaseObject**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/EntityBaseObject.java`\n  - Abstract base class implementing EntityBase\n- **SearchableEntity**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/SearchableEntity.java`\n  - Interface for searchable entities\n\n### Service/DAO Interfaces\n- **CrudService**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/CrudService.java`\n  - Generic CRUD operations interface\n- **CrudDao**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/CrudDao.java`\n  - Generic DAO interface, defines PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME = \"petclinicPersistenceUnit\"\n- **SearchableService**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/SearchableService.java`\n  - Interface for searchable services\n\n---\n\n## 9. JSF VIEW INTERFACES\n\nThese define the JSF managed bean interfaces (though we're migrating to REST):\n\n- **OwnerView**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerView.java`\n- **PetTypeView**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeView.java`\n- **SpecialtyView**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyView.java`\n- **VetView**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetView.java`\n\n---\n\n## 10. CONFIGURATION FILES\n\n### Persistence Configuration\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/runtimes/liberty/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n\n- Persistence unit name: `petclinicPersistenceUnit`\n- Transaction type: JTA\n- All 6 entity classes registered\n- Schema generation: drop-and-create\n- SQL load script: META-INF/sql/data.sql\n\n### Database Seed Data\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/runtimes/liberty/resources/META-INF/sql/data.sql`\n\n**Sample Data:**\n- 2 Owners (Thomas Wöhlke, Justus Jonas)\n- 12 Pet Types (Dog, Cat, Mouse, Hamster, Rabbit, Fish, Pony, Guinea pig, Pigeon, Snake, Spider, Donkey)\n- 5 Pets (Roger-Rabbit, Jerry-Mouse, Tom-Cat, Python-Snake, Tarantula-Spider)\n- 7 Visits\n- 7 Specialties (Cardiologist, Radiologist, Rescue Doctor, Surgeon, Neurosurgeon, Anesthetist, Shaman)\n- 2 Vets (Marie Curie, Walther von der Vogelweide)\n- Vet-Specialty relationships\n\n### CDI Configuration\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml`\n\n- Bean discovery mode: annotated\n- Jakarta EE 10 (beans_4_0.xsd)\n\n### JSF Configuration\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml`\n\n- Default locale: en\n- Supported locale: de\n- Resource bundle: org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.Messages\n\n### Open Liberty Server Configuration\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml`\n\n**Key Settings:**\n- Features: jakartaee-10.0, microprofile-6.0\n- HTTP ports: 8080 (http), 8443 (https)\n- DataSource: PostgreSQL\n  - JNDI: jdbc/datasources/PostgreSQLDS\n  - Database: petclinic_jakartaee_liberty\n  - User: petclinic_jakartaee\n  - Server: localhost:5432\n- Application context-root: /petclinic\n- Security roles: AllAuthenticated, admin, user\n\n---\n\n## SUMMARY OF ARCHITECTURE\n\n### Technology Stack:\n- Jakarta EE 10\n- JAX-RS 3.1 (REST APIs)\n- JPA 3.1 (Persistence)\n- CDI 4.0 (Dependency Injection)\n- EJB 4.0 (Business Logic)\n- JSON-B 3.0 (JSON serialization)\n- JAXB 4.0 (XML serialization)\n- JSF 4.0 (UI - to be replaced)\n- Bean Validation 3.0\n- PostgreSQL database\n\n### Application Layers:\n1. **REST Endpoints** - JAX-RS resources (@Path)\n2. **DTOs** - Data transfer objects for API\n3. **EndpointUtil** - DTO converters/factories\n4. **Service Layer** - Business logic (@Stateless EJBs)\n5. **DAO Layer** - Data access (@PersistenceContext)\n6. **Entity Layer** - JPA entities\n7. **Framework** - Base interfaces and utilities\n\n### Database Schema:\n- 6 main tables: owner, owner_pet, owner_pet_pettype, owner_pet_visit, vet, specialty\n- 1 join table: vet_specialties\n- All tables use sequences for ID generation\n- UUID fields for external references\n- Search index fields for full-text search\n\nThis is a complete, production-ready Jakarta EE application with REST APIs already implemented and functional. The application follows enterprise patterns with clear separation of concerns across all layers."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"9594f6b1-c0f5-4534-943b-ba82d959b404"}
