{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0131Ri9bAmHVFvTFrXV2sur6","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All 6 files have been successfully written for the Quarkus migration. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n## Quarkus Migration Files Written Successfully\n\nAll 6 files have been successfully migrated to Quarkus with the following key changes:\n\n### 1. **Visit.java** \nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java`\n- Removed redundant unique constraint on multiple columns\n- Changed column name constant from `COL_VISIT_DATE` to `COL_DATE`\n- Simplified `getPrimaryKey()` method to return only description\n- Simplified `updateSearchindex()` method with better null handling\n- Removed `optional=false` from `@ManyToOne` annotation\n- Changed `protected Date date` to `private Date date`\n- Added `Serializable` interface\n\n### 2. **VisitDao.java**\nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDao.java`\n- Removed `Serializable` interface and `serialVersionUID`\n- Removed `@NotNull` annotation from method parameter\n- Changed method name to `getVisits(Pet pet)` for consistency\n\n### 3. **VisitDaoImpl.java**\nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java`\n- Replaced `@Stateless` EJB annotation with `@ApplicationScoped` for Quarkus CDI\n- Changed `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject` for EntityManager injection\n- Removed `unitName` parameter from persistence context\n- Added `@Transactional` annotations on write methods\n- Removed `@PostActivate` and `@PrePassivate` EJB lifecycle methods\n- Removed `Serializable` interface\n- Simplified query result handling\n\n### 4. **VisitService.java**\nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitService.java`\n- Removed `Serializable` interface and `serialVersionUID`\n- Changed method name from `getAllVisitsOfAnPet(Pet pet)` to `getVisits(Pet pet)` for consistency\n\n### 5. **VisitServiceImpl.java**\nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitServiceImpl.java`\n- Replaced `@Stateless` EJB annotation with `@ApplicationScoped` for Quarkus CDI\n- Changed `@EJB` to `@Inject` for dependency injection\n- Added `@Transactional` annotations on write methods\n- Removed `Serializable` interface\n- Updated method call to use `getVisits()` instead of previous method name\n- Removed unused imports\n\n### 6. **VisitListener.java**\nPath: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitListener.java`\n- Removed `Serializable` interface and `serialVersionUID`\n- Simplified lifecycle methods to only include `@PrePersist`, `@PreUpdate`, and `@PreRemove`\n- Removed `@PostPersist`, `@PostUpdate`, `@PostRemove`, and `@PostLoad` methods\n- Removed dependency on `EntityListenerLogger.logIt()` method\n- Direct logging with simplified messages\n\nAll files now follow Quarkus patterns using CDI (`@ApplicationScoped`, `@Inject`) instead of EJB (`@Stateless`, `@EJB`), and Jakarta EE standards for persistence and transactions."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"b51eb1a5-70ab-494b-9217-91d612f9ce70"}
