{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Jjiiw4oAbP14d2n9npQqCT","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All 12 DTO files have been successfully written for the Quarkus migration. Let me provide a summary of the changes made.\n\n## Summary\n\nSuccessfully migrated all 12 DTO files for the Quarkus migration. All files have been updated at the base path:\n`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/`\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n\n1. **Replaced Jakarta JSON-B annotations with Jackson annotations:**\n   - `@JsonbProperty` → `@JsonProperty`\n   - `@JsonbDateFormat` → `@JsonFormat`\n   \n2. **Removed JAXB annotations:**\n   - Removed `@XmlRootElement` from all DTOs\n   - Removed all Jakarta XML binding imports\n\n3. **Added Jackson serialization annotations:**\n   - `@JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)` on main entity DTOs (Owner, Pet, PetType, Specialty, Vet, Visit)\n   - Retained `@JsonProperty` with named values where specified (e.g., \"owner\", \"pet\", \"visitList\", \"specialtyList\")\n\n4. **Removed validation annotations:**\n   - Removed `@NotNull`, `@NotEmpty`, `@NotBlank`, `@Pattern`, `@Digits` annotations\n   - These are typically handled at the service/entity layer in Quarkus\n\n5. **Updated Lombok annotations:**\n   - Simplified `@EqualsAndHashCode` (removed `callSuper = false` parameter)\n\n6. **Updated serialVersionUID values:**\n   - Modified values as specified in the new DTOs\n\n### Files Updated:\n\n1. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java`\n2. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java`\n3. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java`\n4. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java`\n5. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java`\n6. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java`\n7. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java`\n8. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java`\n9. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java`\n10. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java`\n11. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java`\n12. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java`\n\nAll DTOs are now compatible with Quarkus and use Jackson for JSON serialization instead of Jakarta JSON-B and JAXB."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"c07de317-8eb9-4151-b52c-a560d74f0fa0"}
