{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01STW6XtTr42bKFArJfKqTRE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All 6 REST Endpoint files have been successfully migrated for Quarkus. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Successfully Written REST Endpoint Files\n\nAll 6 REST Endpoint files have been migrated from Java EE to Quarkus with the following changes:\n\n### Files Written:\n1. **OwnerEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java`\n2. **PetEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java`\n3. **PetTypeEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java`\n4. **SpecialtyEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java`\n5. **VetEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java`\n6. **VisitEndpoint.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java`\n\n### Migration Changes Applied:\n\n1. **Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped`** - Changed from EJB stateless beans to CDI application-scoped beans\n2. **Replaced `@EJB` with `@Inject`** - Changed from EJB injection to CDI dependency injection\n3. **Removed `Serializable` interface** - Eliminated unnecessary serialization for Quarkus\n4. **Removed `serialVersionUID` fields** - No longer needed without Serializable\n5. **Removed JAXB exception handling** - Removed `throws JAXBException` from XML methods (Jackson/JSON-B handles this automatically)\n6. **Removed unused imports** - Cleaned up imports for `jakarta.xml.bind.JAXBException`, `java.io.Serializable`, and other obsolete imports\n7. **Added `@Produces` at class level** - Moved `MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON` to class-level annotation for cleaner code\n8. **Kept JAX-RS annotations** - Preserved `@Path`, `@GET`, `@PathParam`, `@Produces` using `jakarta.ws.rs.*` imports\n9. **Simplified code structure** - Removed unnecessary verbose code while maintaining functionality\n\nAll files have been successfully updated and are ready for Quarkus deployment."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"295d7a3c-fbe4-424e-ac9b-6f5aad9c8c67"}
