{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0185VKRz2EgBDyqos1VfrKi8","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.inject.Inject;\n     4→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     5→import jakarta.ws.rs.GET;\n     6→import jakarta.ws.rs.Path;\n     7→import jakarta.ws.rs.PathParam;\n     8→import jakarta.ws.rs.Produces;\n     9→import jakarta.ws.rs.core.MediaType;\n    10→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n    11→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeDto;\n    12→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeEndpointUtil;\n    13→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.pettype.api.PetTypeListDto;\n    14→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeService;\n    15→\n    16→import java.util.List;\n    17→\n    18→@Log\n    19→@Path(\"/petType\")\n    20→@ApplicationScoped\n    21→@Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)\n    22→public class PetTypeEndpoint {\n    23→\n    24→    @Inject\n    25→    PetTypeService petTypeService;\n    26→\n    27→    @Inject\n    28→    PetTypeEndpointUtil petTypeEndpointUtil;\n    29→\n    30→    @GET\n    31→    @Path(\"/list\")\n    32→    public List<PetTypeDto> getList() {\n    33→        log.info(\"getList\");\n    34→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll()).getPetType();\n    35→    }\n    36→\n    37→    @GET\n    38→    @Path(\"/{id}\")\n    39→    public PetTypeDto getEntity(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    40→        log.info(\"getEntity\");\n    41→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    42→    }\n    43→\n    44→    @GET\n    45→    @Path(\"/list+json\")\n    46→    public List<PetTypeDto> getListAsJson() {\n    47→        log.info(\"getListAsJson\");\n    48→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll()).getPetType();\n    49→    }\n    50→\n    51→    @GET\n    52→    @Path(\"/{id}+json\")\n    53→    public PetTypeDto getEntityAsJson(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    54→        log.info(\"getEntityAsJson\");\n    55→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    56→    }\n    57→\n    58→    @GET\n    59→    @Path(\"/list+xml\")\n    60→    public PetTypeListDto getListAsXml() {\n    61→        log.info(\"getListAsXml\");\n    62→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petTypeService.getAll());\n    63→    }\n    64→\n    65→    @GET\n    66→    @Path(\"/{id}+xml\")\n    67→    public PetTypeDto getEntityAsXml(@PathParam(\"id\") Long id) {\n    68→        log.info(\"getEntityAsXml\");\n    69→        return petTypeEndpointUtil.dtoFactory(petTypeService.findById(id));\n    70→    }\n    71→}\n    72→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"dc2068c5-837c-433f-b925-dec1a1973b4a"}
