{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JbVFVNLCZWxqKqeBBHizbP","type":"tool_result","content":"Waiting for application at http://localhost:33803 ...\nApplication is ready!\n\n=== PetClinic Quarkus Smoke Tests ===\n\n--- Owner Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/owner/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/owner/1 returns a single owner\n  PASS GET /rest/owner/list+json returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/owner/1+json returns JSON owner\n\n--- Pet Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/pet/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/pet/1 returns a single pet\n  PASS GET /rest/pet/list+json returns JSON array\n\n--- PetType Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/petType/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/petType/1 returns a single petType\n  PASS GET /rest/petType/list+json returns JSON array\n\n--- Specialty Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/specialty/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/specialty/1 returns a single specialty\n  PASS GET /rest/specialty/list+json returns JSON array\n\n--- Vet Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/vet/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/vet/1 returns a single vet\n  PASS GET /rest/vet/list+json returns JSON array\n\n--- Visit Endpoints ---\n  PASS GET /rest/visit/list returns JSON array\n  PASS GET /rest/visit/1 returns a single visit\n  PASS GET /rest/visit/list+json returns JSON array\n\n--- Data Integrity Checks ---\n  PASS Owner list has at least 2 owners\n  PASS PetType list has at least 12 pet types\n  PASS Specialty list has at least 7 specialties\n  PASS Vet list has at least 2 vets\n\n=== Results: 23 passed, 0 failed out of 23 tests ===","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"e794ac11-c1c4-4e33-a367-0b56e5cc3dd4"}
