{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VvXhVuTs259QHPrsxDreZA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Jakarta EE 10 to Quarkus 3.8.4 migration is complete. Here's a summary:\n\n## Migration Complete\n\n**Result: 23/23 smoke tests passed**\n\n### What was done:\n1. **Build system**: Rewrote `pom.xml` from Jakarta EE/Liberty WAR to Quarkus 3.8.4 JAR packaging\n2. **Configuration**: Replaced Liberty `server.xml` with Quarkus `application.properties`\n3. **CDI/EJB**: `@Stateless` -> `@ApplicationScoped`, `@EJB` -> `@Inject`, added `@Transactional`\n4. **Persistence**: `@PersistenceContext(unitName=...)` -> `@Inject EntityManager`\n5. **Serialization**: JSON-B/JAXB annotations -> Jackson (`@JsonProperty`, `@JsonFormat`)\n6. **REST endpoints**: Adapted for RESTEasy Reactive, removed JAXB exception handling\n7. **Removed JSF**: All views, converters, flow views, message bundles (Quarkus doesn't support JSF)\n8. **Dockerfile**: Updated to build and run Quarkus fast-jar format\n9. **Seed data**: Migrated to `import.sql` for Quarkus Hibernate ORM\n\n### Errors fixed:\n- Wrong import package in `PetTypeEndpoint.java` (missing `.petclinic.` segment)\n- Uber-jar config not applied; switched to Quarkus default fast-jar format"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":552,"cache_read_input_tokens":77351,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":552,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":374},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","uuid":"6a9e7846-69fb-4f80-9908-8ca05096b064"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2397427,"duration_api_ms":2678874,"num_turns":82,"result":"The Jakarta EE 10 to Quarkus 3.8.4 migration is complete. Here's a summary:\n\n## Migration Complete\n\n**Result: 23/23 smoke tests passed**\n\n### What was done:\n1. **Build system**: Rewrote `pom.xml` from Jakarta EE/Liberty WAR to Quarkus 3.8.4 JAR packaging\n2. **Configuration**: Replaced Liberty `server.xml` with Quarkus `application.properties`\n3. **CDI/EJB**: `@Stateless` -> `@ApplicationScoped`, `@EJB` -> `@Inject`, added `@Transactional`\n4. **Persistence**: `@PersistenceContext(unitName=...)` -> `@Inject EntityManager`\n5. **Serialization**: JSON-B/JAXB annotations -> Jackson (`@JsonProperty`, `@JsonFormat`)\n6. **REST endpoints**: Adapted for RESTEasy Reactive, removed JAXB exception handling\n7. **Removed JSF**: All views, converters, flow views, message bundles (Quarkus doesn't support JSF)\n8. **Dockerfile**: Updated to build and run Quarkus fast-jar format\n9. **Seed data**: Migrated to `import.sql` for Quarkus Hibernate ORM\n\n### Errors fixed:\n- Wrong import package in `PetTypeEndpoint.java` (missing `.petclinic.` segment)\n- Uber-jar config not applied; switched to Quarkus default fast-jar format","session_id":"c5bd7990-ebbe-4b4c-8bc8-ce64a20596ca","total_cost_usd":24.78998808000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":204,"cache_creation_input_tokens":206830,"cache_read_input_tokens":5821691,"output_tokens":65136,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":206830}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":393773,"outputTokens":12048,"cacheReadInputTokens":307556,"cacheCreationInputTokens":35356,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.42317087999999997,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":996,"outputTokens":128689,"cacheReadInputTokens":1572434,"cacheCreationInputTokens":39353